nodes.text: Duel at unidentified Outer Rim spaceport

A duel took place at an Outer Rim spaceport during the Clone Wars, when two Jedi clashed with the renegade Sith Lord Maul and Savage Opress. It was one in a series of raids committed by the brothers after the massacre they perpetrated on Raydonia. They concluded the duel by killing the two Jedi.
